道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=70fe8b74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"20870e93f6063af21130c57d9c16a93d6ac1bbb0","tid":1004104,"uid":218954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"450b505b46e79712bef5b77b56f77e3d5f8c25f9","tid":1004104,"uid":226612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"592dbcf797fa1d9e703357e28d2fbb72cc38ccb8","tid":1004104,"uid":162295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:53:13.000Z","msg":"今日都病發，特登落街行下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"我係屋企攤左一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"絲讀書定做緊嘢？<br />\n我成日一發作就射波<br />\n有時嚴重嗰排仲會resign，搞到cv花晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但喺屋企嗰陣又會覺得自己好廢，咩都做唔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80550a686bedb77d84ac436d1cfcd2105570909","tid":1004104,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T16:03:54.000Z","msg":"每個月都會嚟一次,男人老狗搞到好似嚟M咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51fea0f6352815f02da6d63a4760891bbcddb49","tid":1004104,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80550a686bedb77d84ac436d1cfcd2105570909","tid":1004104,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply